            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Labor Crisis</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            <span class="font-bold text-primary-600">99%</span> of operators report higher labor costs. 
            Without data-driven scheduling, you're burning out staff and wasting money.
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 italic">
            Median labor: 36.5% of sales (full-service)
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="stagger-item card-entrance bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-50 to-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-primary-100 hover-lift">
