          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            <span class="font-bold text-primary-600">70%</span> of guests never return after their first visit. 
            You have no CRM, no guest data, no way to bring them back.
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 italic">
            Lost lifetime value: thousands per guest
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="mt-12 text-center bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-50 to-primary-100 p-8 rounded-2xl">
