                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-700"><strong>Phase 3 - The FOH:</strong> CRM, loyalty, and first-party ordering to drive repeat business</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-500 mr-3 flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
